reviewText: This was one of the classic TV shows that I had to own.  It is nice to see the gang back as I take a stroll down memory lane.  It would have been nice if there were extras and if they spent some time remastering the series, but who can complain about the series being on DVD so true fans can watch how this sizzling show ends?
summary: Superior TV series wraps up in the final season
Title: Melrose Place: The Seventh and Final Season, Vol. 2
